snippet.title: KIS KISKO PYAAR KAROON 2: Official Trailer | Kapil Sharma, Manjot Singh |In Cinemas 12 December 2025
snippet.description:
Kapil Sharma is back with his clean comedy capers and how 🎬🤣 
Presenting the official trailer of 'Kis Kisko Pyaar Karoon 2', starring Kapil Sharma, Manjot Singh, Hira Warina, Tridha Choudhary, Parul Gulati and others. This is a sequel to the blockbuster 'Kis Kisko Pyaar Karoon', Kapil Sharma's debut film.  #KisKiskoPyaarKaroon2 #KapilSharma #ManjotSingh 

Experience this laugh riot with your entire family in cinemas on 12th December 2025 🤣🤣

snippet.title: The Lost Chapter: Yuki’s Revenge | Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Quentin Tarantino had a dream of a Kill Bill chapter that never made it to the silver screen, a chapter known as “Yuki’s Revenge.” Over 20 years later, Tarantino and Epic have come together to bring the story to life in Fortnite. 

Tarantino’s The Lost Chapter: Yuki’s Revenge stars Uma Thurman and premieres in Fortnite on November 30 at 2 PM ET! Doors open 30 minutes before the show starts. #fortnite #fortniteseven

snippet.title: Aukaat Ke Bahar - Official Trailer ft. Elvish Yadav, Nikhil Vijay, Malhaar Rathod | Amazon MX Player
snippet.description:
Amazon MX Player presents 
Aukaat Ke Bahar - Official Trailer

Starring: Elvish Yadav, Malhaar Rathod, Nikhil Vijay, Hetal Gada, Rohan Khurrana, Keshav Sadhna
Production House: Rusk Studios
Produced By: Rusk Media Pvt. Ltd.
Directed By: Tanmai Rastogi
Developed, Story, Screenplay and Written by: Jayati Pandya, Akhilesh Vats, Jasmeet Bhatia, Ayush Gaur, Sumbul Khan, Siddharth Saini

Genre: Drama Romance
 
About Aukaat Ke Bahar: Rajveer Ahlawat, a small-town boxer from Safidon, enters Delhi’s elite St. Collins college to fulfill his brother’s dream of becoming a polished, English-speaking graduate. Amidst bullies, culture shocks, and class divides, he falls for Antara Shukla — a senior with political aspirations and far out of his league. When a humiliating dare collides with his growing feelings and a family crisis back home, Rajveer must fight harder than ever — this time, not for glory, but for love, dignity, and survival.

About Amazon MX Player
Amazon MX Player is India’s leading free, premium, ad-supported entertainment service in India. It offers a diverse range of award-winning web series, reality shows, popular international shows, and a massive movie library across multiple genres. With a strong focus on original content, Amazon MX Player has launched some of the largest shows in India, which includes Ek Badnaam Aashram, Campus Diaries, Jamnapaar, Half CA, Bhaukaal, Raktanchal, Dehati Ladke, Who’s your Gynac, Sixer, Hip Hop India, Hunter – Totega Nahi Todega and more. Amazon MX Player also offers a rich selection of international content dubbed in Hindi, Tamil, and Telugu under MX Vdesi, featuring popular shows like What's Wrong With Secretary Kim?, Daydreamer, Gangnam Beauty, My Girlfriend Is An Alien, Put Your Head On My Shoulder, Our Story, and more!

snippet.title: Mount & Blade II: Bannerlord - War Sails - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Set Sail for Glory - War Sails has arrived!

The seas of Calradia open today with the release of War Sails, the epic single-player expansion for Mount & Blade II: Bannerlord.

Sail the high seas, lead mighty fleets, and forge your legacy as you command powerful ships, engage in thrilling naval battles, and master maritime conquest. Embark on daring adventures across new territories with fresh mechanics, dangerous challenges, and a fully realized naval progression system. Customize your fleet, conquer coastal settlements, and carve your legend on the open waters.

Today, we're also releasing our v1.3.4 base game update which introduces many new mechanics like alliances & trade agreements, stealth & disguise, fast mode, and much more. You can read the full patch notes here - https://www.taleworlds.com/en/News/587

War Sails is out now on PlayStation 5, Xbox Series X|S, and PC (Steam, Epic Games Store, GOG). 10% off for the first 2 weeks!

snippet.title: JUJUTSU KAISEN: Execution | Official English Trailer - In Theatres December 5
snippet.description:
JUJUTSU KAISEN: Execution
From MAPPA
Based on the Shonen Jump manga by Gege Akutami

The best of the Shibuya Incident arc combines with the debut of the first two episodes of Season 3's Culling Game arc in this exclusive theatrical event!

Screenings available in both Japanese w/ English subtitles and English dub in theatres nationwide starting December 5

Follow @GKIDSFilms for more updates!
https://brnw.ch/21wXP7a

A veil abruptly descends over the busy Shibuya area amid the bustling Halloween crowds, trapping countless civilians inside. Satoru Gojo, the strongest jujutsu sorcerer, steps into the chaos. But lying in wait are curse users and spirits scheming to seal him away.

Yuji Itadori, accompanied by his classmates and other top-tier jujutsu sorcerers, enters the fray in an unprecedented clash of curses — the Shibuya Incident.

In the aftermath, ten colonies across Japan are transformed into dens of curses in a plan orchestrated by Noritoshi Kamo, the most wicked sorcerer in history. As the deadly Culling Game starts, Special Grade sorcerer Yuta Okkotsu is assigned to carry out Yuji’s execution for his perceived crimes.

The desperate confrontation between Satoru Gojo’s two beloved students comes to the big screen with an early preview. Be the first to experience Yuji and Yuta’s fateful battle with the hotly anticipated kickoff to Season 3 in theatres nationwide.

snippet.title: GOAT – New Trailer (HD)
snippet.description:
He’s about to change the game. 

From the artists that made KPop Demon Hunters, Spider-Man: Across the #SpiderVerse, and producer Stephen Curry, #GOATmovie is exclusively in movie theatres February 2026.

Visit our site: https://goat.movie/
Find your team: https://theroarleague.com/

Follow Us on Social:
https://www.instagram.com/goatmovieofficial
https://www.facebook.com/goatmovieofficial
https://www.tiktok.com/@goatmovieofficial
https://x.com/the_goat_movie

Subscribe for more exclusive content: https://www.youtube.com/@sonypictures

From Sony Pictures Animation, the studio behind Spider-ManTM: Across the Spider-Verse and the artists that made KPop Demon Hunters, comes GOAT, an original action-comedy set in an all-animal world. The story follows Will, a small goat with big dreams who gets a once-in-a-lifetime shot to join the pros and play roarball – a high-intensity, co-ed, full-contact sport dominated by the fastest, fiercest animals in the world. Will’s new teammates aren’t thrilled about having a little goat on their roster, but Will is determined to revolutionize the sport and prove once and for all that “smalls can ball!”
 
Directed by:​​
Tyree Dillihay
 
Co-Directed by: 
​​Adam Rosette​
 
Written by:​​
Aaron Buchsbaum & Teddy Riley
 
Inspired by the book “Funky Dunks” by Chris Tougas
 
Produced by: ​​​​
Michelle Raimo Kouyate
Rodney Rothman
​​​​​Adam Rosenberg
​​​​​Stephen Curry and Erick Peyton
     
Executive Producers:​​​
Rick Mischel
​​​​​Fonda Snyder
 
Cast:​​​​​
Caleb McLaughlin
Gabrielle Union
Stephen Curry
Nicola Coughlan
Nick Kroll
David Harbour
Jenifer Lewis
Aaron Pierre
Patton Oswalt
Andrew Santino
Bobby Lee
Eduardo Franco
Sherry Cola
Jelly Roll
Jennifer Hudson
 
Credits not final
